Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,白祭上大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 就我们五个人吗
